The job I love.
Hey my name is Rami, I'm from Biet Jan, I want to express my job to the children in the village. My job is a volunteer in my village, we do many things like fixing the village and cleaning it, and we do many things to the children like dancing and we give them gifts and many things. I would to do a game to the children and give them gifts. I enjoy my job because of the volunteer work, I like to give the other.